💡 Placement Tip

In placement aptitude tests, Surds & Indices questions mainly focus on index laws, simplifying surds, fractional and negative exponents, and rationalisation. Memorize the laws of indices, recognize perfect squares, and practice using conjugates for rationalisation. With these techniques, most placement-level questions can be solved in under one minute.
